1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Libraries – State Library Resource Center – Funding
3 FOR the purpose of altering the calculation of certain funding for the State Library
4 Resource Center for certain fiscal years; and generally relating to the State Library
5 Resource Center.
6 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
